author: Warhammer
description:
2024 has been a fantastic year for Warhammer and for painting! There have been so many great new releases and we’ve all had so much fun. As the year comes to a close, we thought it would be a cool idea to ask each paint presenter which was their favourite miniature to paint this year. 

What is your favourite miniature of 2024? Let us know in the comments!
